cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper proposes a deep neural network-based architecture for indoor positioning using RGB images and point clouds. This involves scene classification, RGB to point cloud conversion, and position regression. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves geometric reasoning, which could fall under computer graphics (cs.GR).
